### CCR-017 §3 — BlindDetailType enum + Late Reg
###
### 검증:
### - blind-structures level 추가 시 BlindDetailType enum 검증
### - Late Reg 계산식 정합

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 63.1 GET /blind-structures — 목록
GET {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 + envelope { data: [...], error: null }

### 63.2 GET /blind-structures/{id}/levels — levels (BlindDetailType enum 포함)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/1/levels
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 + envelope { data: [{ levelNo, smallBlind, ..., detailType: 'normal'|'break'|'breakIn' }], error }

### 63.3 POST /blind-structures/{id}/levels — break level 추가
POST {{host}}/api/v1/blind-structures/1/levels
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "levelNo": 999,
  "smallBlind": 0,
  "bigBlind": 0,
  "ante": 0,
  "durationMinutes": 10,
  "detailType": "break"
}

# 예상: 201 + envelope (또는 422 if blind structure 없음)
